Class NetworkTab

java.lang.Object
  unr.neurotranslate.ui.NetworkTab

public class NetworkTab
extends java.lang.Object

The NetworkTab class is responsible for handling all the Network tab layout and widgets. A Table layout is used in order to hold all the widgets used in this tab.
